<br>
America has never really gotten over this, so you see us making a big deal over showing a bare ass or mild swearing on broadcast television.  Meanwhile, we have cable tv and a huge pornography industry.  Yet in other countries, nekkid people aren't all that uncommon on broadcast tv<br>
<br>
A significant portion of the American population is rather religious, and perhaps they still wield more influence than is the case in another country.  However, there are crooks in any religious organization..so the American who goes to church but steals from his friend could be anyone, anywhere in the world.<br>
